The public welfare net red coffee shop hidden in the small street has lived in Siem Reap, Cambodia, for more than half a year, and has been listening to friends Amway The Little Red Fox Espresso Food and its public welfare deeds. After a long time of curiosity, it was finally empty. The low-key "Little Red Fox" Little Red Fox Coffee Shop is hidden on a small street in the city center, and the surrounding area is very quiet and a bit difficult to find. At the main entrance of the store, there are many potted plants with large leaves (I mistakenly thought it was a flower shop at first), and the tables and chairs are the kind of very literary red with a sense of age. On the wall where the door was entered, there were books for the shopkeepers to read, and then the aisle, on the other side of the wall, there were three tables, and there were several pastoral oil paintings on the aisle wall. Take the stairs to the second floor, continue to walk to the innermost cabin, the light is getting dimmer, a glass coffee table is placed in the middle of the cabin, three sofas and two lazy chairs are placed around the coffee table, a yellow light lamp, I suddenly felt that the cabin was suitable for my otagonist's environment. I sat on a lazy chair with my ass, followed the waiter behind to see me seated, immediately smiled, asked me what to drink, and a cup of the store's special unsweetened latte. Taste food I think, the reason for this store fire is mainly that the decoration style can hook people's petty bourgeoisie and their boss's public welfare; of course, the food in the store is enough to attract people, the most popular in the store is latte and apple yogurt. The dense milk bubble is very good to blend the bitter taste of espresso, it is worthy of a strong latte. For ladies, I recommend apple yogurt. The yogurt here is made by the boss himself. I heard from friends who often come. The apple sour grandmother is rich in fragrance and has a weight loss beauty effect. ※ Warm reminder business hours: 6:00—24:00 Recommended food: Latte coffee, coconut coffee, apple yogurt, cheese berries, fruit salad, red wine

Check in on the beautiful island of East Africa 🏖 on this "lonest restaurant in the world" If there is anything you must not miss on Zanzibar, I really can't blurt out. But if you let me say the restaurant that you can't miss the most, it's not The Rock Restaurant . 🌊 Unique Location 🌊 This restaurant, known as the world's loneliest restaurant, is very eye-catching in its location alone it is built on a rock, located in the blue Atlantic Ocean, with the world's most invincible 360-degree sea view! This unique geographical location has made it one of the symbols of Zanzibar Island, and it has also become a must-see place for Internet celebrities around the world. How should guests reach the restaurant when they choose such a "lonely" location? Interestingly, the way to go will vary according to the high tide or low tide, when the water level is lowered, the road to the restaurant will be exposed naked, and the restaurant will also spread sandbags on the bare road, then you can walk directly from the beach to The Rock. At high tide, the restaurant arranges boats to pick up guests, and of course, if you want, no one will stop you. I was on the boat when I went, and the boatman on the restaurant side was not so much a rower, but rather a boater, who pulled us over. 🏚 Restaurant Landscape 🏚The Rock2010 began construction and officially opened in 2012. The decoration style is the original ecological style with local characteristics. The restaurant has 12 tables, which can allow up to 45 people to eat at the same time. Here you can choose to enjoy a seafood meal indoors or sit on an outdoor sofa and enjoy Zanzibar’s priceless treasuresthe colorful, invincible sea view that hits the heart. Listening to the waves, the sea breeze is blowing, surrounded by the blue and green sea, the mouth is enjoying a fresh seafood feast, try to ask, is there anything more dreamy than this?

name: Taste of Khmer Soup and BBQ

reviews.comment: Cambodian food is recommended, the first meal of the super delicious Cambodian hot pot in every place is the first impression of this city. It seems that encountering appetizing food in a foreign country is more than anything. The first night I arrived in Siem Reap, I went to eat a Cambodian hot pot recommended by my friends. As a girl who likes to eat hot pot, I was really surprised by this authentic Cambodian hot pot. 🔸 Eating method: Cambodian hot pot is different from Sichuan hot pot and copper hot pot that we often eat in China, but is more similar to Thai hot pot. The middle is a raised barbecue part of the barbecue, and the surrounding area is poured water to cook vegetables. This is more similar to the "water fried meat" that we often eat in China. 💡 The locals call this hot pot: "Niu Shangshan" hot pot, which is quite apt ～🔸 dishes: What is more surprising is that the variety of Siem Reap dishes is quite complete, all kinds of vegetables are complete, as well as golden needle mushrooms, apricot mushrooms, green peppers, sweet potatoes, etc. It is not easy to know that you want to eat rich vegetables abroad. ❗️ Super recommended beef! The beef is wrapped in a layer of eggs. After roasting on a roasting tray, it is really delicious. In addition to beef, pork and so on are also very good. ▻ Very interesting is that the hot pot package here also includes instant noodles, I feel very kind and grounded, and then the food is very fragrant and haha ～🔸 The focus is on their home marinade, the taste is not strange, and the unexpected compound Chinese taste, sour and hot and hot like it very much. In chatting with the boss, I learned that his family's marinade was made by his mother. It should be regarded as their "secret recipe". In addition to hot pot barbecue, this store also has Chinese and Cambodian meals to choose from. ❣️ Service: The store owner is very friendly and likes the Chinese very much. I really want to sigh that Cambodia is really a very friendly country to China. The boss and waiter will worry about helping to order food, barbecue, etc. throughout the whole process. The whole experience is still great. ❣️ Store name: TASTE OF KHMER SOUP&BBQ, just search directly in Google Maps.
